Class GenericDeploymentUnitDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.api.management.GenericDeploymentUnitDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeploymentUnitDefinition

    public class GenericDeploymentUnitDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
implements DeploymentUnitDefinition
    Represents a deployment unit which contains proxy services, endpoints, sequences etc. Supposed to be used by programmatic interaction with the UltraESB runtime via the ServerAdmin API.

    2.0.0
